{#- Changelog — tabular rendering.

    One row per version; most recent first. Inline delta cells use the
    `+A / ~C / -R` shorthand (added / changed / resolved). A detail block
    immediately below the table enumerates T-IDs for the latest entry
    (capped at `_max`) so the most recent run is easy to audit without
    scrolling the table horizontally.

    Data shape per entry (see schemas/threat-model.output.schema.yaml):
      version, date, mode, baseline_sha, current_sha
      added:    { threats: [T-NNN,...], components: [C-NN,...], attack_surface: [E-NN,...] }
      changed:  { threats: [T-NNN,...], notes_by_id: { T-NNN: "..." } }
      resolved: { threats: [T-NNN,...], reason_by_id: { T-NNN: "..." } }
      reanalyzed_components, carried_forward_components, changed_files, note
-#}
{%- set _max = 10 -%}
## Changelog

_Append-only history of assessment runs. Most recent first._

| Version | Date | Mode | Baseline → Current | Δ Threats | Components | Note |
|---------|------|------|--------------------|-----------|------------|------|
{%- for entry in changelog %}
{%- set v             = entry.version -%}
{%- set date          = entry.date or '—' -%}
{%- set mode          = (entry.mode or 'full') | lower -%}
{%- set baseline_sha  = entry.baseline_sha or '' -%}
{%- set current_sha   = entry.current_sha or '' -%}
{%- set has_baseline  = (baseline_sha | length) > 0 -%}
{%- set short_base    = baseline_sha[:7] -%}
{%- set short_cur     = current_sha[:7] if current_sha else '—' -%}
{%- set added_t       = (entry.added.threats   if entry.added   else []) | default([]) -%}
{%- set changed_t     = (entry.changed.threats if entry.changed else []) | default([]) -%}
{%- set resolved_t    = (entry.resolved.threats if entry.resolved else []) | default([]) -%}
{%- set reanalyzed    = entry.reanalyzed_components or [] -%}
{%- set carried       = entry.carried_forward_components or [] -%}
{%- set note          = (entry.note or '') | trim -%}
{%- if note|length > 90 -%}{%- set note = note[:88] ~ '…' -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if note -%}{%- set note = note | replace('|', '\\|') -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- set delta_cell = '+' ~ (added_t|length) ~ ' / ~' ~ (changed_t|length) ~ ' / -' ~ (resolved_t|length) -%}
{%- if has_baseline -%}
{%- set sha_cell = '`' ~ short_base ~ '` → `' ~ short_cur ~ '`' -%}
{%- elif v == 1 and mode == 'full' -%}
{%- set sha_cell = '_(initial)_' -%}
{%- else -%}
{%- set sha_cell = '—' -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- set comp_parts = [] -%}
{%- if reanalyzed -%}{%- set _ = comp_parts.append((reanalyzed|length)|string ~ ' reanalyzed') -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if carried   -%}{%- set _ = comp_parts.append((carried|length)|string ~ ' carried') -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- set comp_cell = comp_parts | join(', ') if comp_parts else '—' -%}
| v{{ v }} | {{ date }} | {{ mode }} | {{ sha_cell }} | {{ delta_cell }} | {{ comp_cell }} | {{ note or '—' }} |
{%- endfor %}

{%- set latest = changelog[0] if changelog else None -%}
{%- if latest %}
{%- set l_added   = (latest.added.threats   if latest.added   else []) | default([]) -%}
{%- set l_changed = (latest.changed.threats if latest.changed else []) | default([]) -%}
{%- set l_resolved= (latest.resolved.threats if latest.resolved else []) | default([]) -%}
{%- if l_added or l_changed or l_resolved %}

**Details v{{ latest.version }}:**
{%- if l_added %}
- **Added ({{ l_added|length }}):** {% for tid in l_added[:_max] %}[{{ tid }}](#{{ tid|lower }}){% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}{% if (l_added|length) > _max %}, +{{ (l_added|length) - _max }} more{% endif %}
{%- endif %}
{%- if l_changed %}
- **Changed ({{ l_changed|length }}):** {% for tid in l_changed[:_max] %}[{{ tid }}](#{{ tid|lower }}){% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}{% if (l_changed|length) > _max %}, +{{ (l_changed|length) - _max }} more{% endif %}
{%- endif %}
{%- if l_resolved %}
- **Resolved ({{ l_resolved|length }}):** {% for tid in l_resolved[:_max] %}[{{ tid }}](#{{ tid|lower }}){% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}{% if (l_resolved|length) > _max %}, +{{ (l_resolved|length) - _max }} more{% endif %}
{%- endif %}
{%- endif %}
{%- endif %}
